Use Case 1 : Initialize bare [S] & [G]

1.1 [S] is initialized
1.2 [G] is initialized
1.3 [G] performs handshaking with [S]
1.3.A If [S] not initialized [G] waits
1.4 [S] sends information to [G] when initialized
